<p>There have also been various guest editors over the years, such as <a href="/wiki/Elton_John" title="Elton John">Elton John</a> on 1 December 2010, <a href="/wiki/The_Body_Shop" title="The Body Shop">The Body Shop</a>'s <a href="/wiki/Anita_Roddick" title="Anita Roddick">Anita Roddick</a> on 19 June 2003 and <a href="/wiki/U2" title="U2">U2</a>'s <a href="/wiki/Bono" title="Bono">Bono</a> in 2006.<sup id="cite&#95;ref-80" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-80"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>80<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup><sup id="cite&#95;ref-81" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-81"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>81<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup><sup id="cite&#95;ref-82" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-82"><span class="cite-bracket">&#91;</span>82<span class="cite-bracket">&#93;</span></a></sup>
</p>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id="Writers_and_columnists">Writers and columnists</h3><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=The_Independent&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Edit section: Writers and columnists"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
